OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMicrosoft's Activision     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftakeover blocked in UK     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Microsoft's $68.7bn (#55bn) deal to buy
OL,6, US video game company Activision       
OL,7, Blizzard has been blocked in the UK by 
OL,8, the Competition and Markets Authority. 
OL,10,FThe proposed takeover would see        
OL,11,FMicrosoft acquire such hit titles as   
OL,12,FCall of Duty and Candy Crush.          
OL,14,FBut the regulator said it was concerned
OL,15,Fthe deal would offer reduced innovation
OL,16,Fand less choice for gamers in the      
OL,17,Ffast-growing cloud gaming business.    
OL,19,FMicrosoft and Activision hit out at the
OL,20,Fdecision and said they would appeal.   
